def sortedSquares(nums):
    squares_list = []
    for i in range(len(nums)):
        square = nums[i] * nums[i]
        squares_list.append(square)
    sorted_squares_list = sorted(squares_list)
    print(sorted_squares_list)
    return sorted_squares_list
